item.title: CENTRO EDUCATIVO NEMI "Apoya Sus Sueños"
item.description:
CENTRO EDUCATIVO NEMI "Apoya Sus Sueños"

Here's another social project. These ones I love. I like documentaries; I like working with children; I like to help more kids get access to the education they deserve. This is about an education center in Mexico City where they give low-income families the opportunity for quality, private-school-class education.

item.title: Intel at 10nm ... a conversation with Mark Bohr of Intel
item.description:
Intel at 10nm ... a conversation with Mark Bohr of Intel

Intel's Process Architecture and Integration team have done what many have said couldn't be done: the first true 10nm in production. They have scaled another node with greater density and performance-per-watt. Most importantly, they did all this with lower cost-per-transistor. In other words, Moore's Law is still alive and well.
